	<BaseGameText>
		<!-- BUILDINGS -->
		<Row Tag="LOC_BUILDING_COAL_POWER_PLANT_UPGRADE_NAME">
			<Text>Coal Power Plant Upgrade</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="LOC_BUILDING_COAL_POWER_PLANT_UPGRADE_DESCRIPTION">
			<Text>+1 [LOC_Tourism] Tourism and all tiles in this City gain +1 Appeal.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="LOC_BUILDING_FOSSIL_FUEL_POWER_PLANT_UPGRADE_NAME">
			<Text>Oil Power Plant Upgrade</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="LOC_BUILDING_FOSSIL_FUEL_POWER_PLANT_UPGRADE_DESCRIPTION">
			<Text>Scientific research conducted here generates +1 [LOC_GreatScientist] Great Scientist point. Bonus Amenity extends to each city center within 9 tiles.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="LOC_BUILDING_NUCLEAR_POWER_PLANT_UPGRADE_NAME"> <!-- building is actually BUILDING_POWER_PLANT -->
			<Text>Nuclear Power Plant Upgrade</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="LOC_BUILDING_NUCLEAR_POWER_PLANT_UPGRADE_DESCRIPTION">
			<Text>All [LOC_Tourism] Tourism yields are increased +10%. Bonus Amenity extends to each city center within 9 tiles.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="LOC_BUILDING_HYDROELECTRIC_DAM_UPGRADE_NAME">
			<Text>Hydroelectric Dam Upgrade</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="LOC_BUILDING_HYDROELECTRIC_DAM_UPGRADE_DESCRIPTION">
			<Text>Bigger market can service more food providers. Plantations and Pastures in this city gain +2 [LOC_Food] Food each. Can only be built once in a city, even if the city has multiple Neighborhoods.</Text>
		</Row>
		<!-- UNIQUES -->
		<Row Tag="LOC_BUILDING_GRAND_BAZAAR_UPGRADE_NAME">
			<Text>Grand Bazaar Upgrade</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="LOC_BUILDING_GRAND_BAZAAR_UPGRADE_DESCRIPTION">
			<Text>A building upgrade unique to the Ottomans. Luxury goods bring more tourists and improve revenues. Increases +2 [LOC_Tourism] Tourism in this city. Luxury Resources in this city gain +2 [LOC_Gold] Gold each. Can only be built once in a city, even if the city has multiple Neighborhoods.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="LOC_BUILDING_THERMAL_BATH_UPGRADE_NAME">
			<Text>Thermal Bath Upgrade</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="LOC_BUILDING_THERMAL_BATH_UPGRADE_DESCRIPTION">
			<Text>A building upgrade unique to Hungary. Grants +1 [LOC_GreatGeneral] Great General point and +2 [LOC_Production] Production from Pastures. May not be built in an Encampment district that already has a Barracks.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="LOC_BUILDING_MARAE_UPGRADE_NAME">
			<Text>Marae Upgrade</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="LOC_BUILDING_MARAE_UPGRADE_DESCRIPTION">
			<Text>A building upgrade unique to the MƒÅori. It seems that your engineers outperformed themsels. This upgrade increases the strength of your outer defenses to the (really) highest possible level. Provides +1 [LOC_Housing] Housing, +1 [LOC_Amenities] Amenity and +1 [LOC_Faith] Faith.</Text>
		</Row>
	</BaseGameText>
	
